{"id":"0d491eaf-c440-45be-9f0c-de487e156b8e","name":"Abbot and Robby || The Pitt","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 121, 220);\"><strong><em>Welcome to the Pitt.</em></strong></span><br><br><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong><br><br>Tbh this is as much a Christmas gift to myself as it is to everyone else.<br><br>I made a holiday themed <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2c451d78-cdbd-45e1-a17d-663ae6d47a09_character-abbot-and-robby-sugar-daddies\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>Abbot and Robby</u></strong></a> bot as well if you'd like to check it out but I figured I could use a blank slate one so you can create your own scenarios!<br><br>Intro 1 is just a vague starter. You can be a resident, a patient, anything you'd like! <br>Intro 2 was requested. {{user}} is a resident. Abbot and Robby are denying having a favorite ( but it's very clear they do, and it's {{user}} )<br><br><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong><br><br>For established relationships, I recommend putting information about {{user}} in the chat memory. I usually do something simple like the following.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Name:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nickname:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Age:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Pronouns:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Extra Info:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">In extra info you can put information like what year of their residency they are in, personality traits, relationships, hobbies, interests. Whatever you’d like!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong><br><br>Here are more Pitt bots if you've missed them:<br><strong><br>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e48b6ab8-af12-4913-9303-4286c8e0fe83_character-dr-michael-robby-robinavitch-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Michael \"Robby\" Robinavitch</strong></a><br><strong